es, significantly boosting work efficiency.',3,'1','0','1',2,0,2025,'年底',''),(418,'10105050','AI的工作項目','AI for RF certification label confirmation','Initially, provided platforms\' label drawing to establish the database of Deep Learning and Image Recognition. \rMaintained ongoing communication with relevant team members to exchange ideas and requirements.','We are now focusing on comparing the \"RMN\" information within certification labels. This initiative aims to enhance the efficiency and accuracy of the daily label confirmation process, as well as provide feedback to further optimize them.','Continuously exploring and conceptualizing image recognition applications, while identifying opportunities to integrate AI into our certification workflows.',3,'1','1','0',2,0,2025,'年底',''),(419,'10105050','AI的工作項目','AI Cybersecurity label documents','AI Cybersecurity label completed 90%, optimize further with user feedback and platform features.','After the initial tool sharing session, I worked to address and resolve the issues item by item, incorporating feedback from my colleagues who are software experts.','Assisted team members in brainstorming ideas for an AI tool and provided fine-tuning suggestions during its development. In Q4, supported the finalization and integration of the tool with the certification team\'s utility.',3,'1','0','1',2,0,2025,'年底',''),(420,'10105050','加分工作項目','Resource Integration & Value Creation','Managed platform/module reports and certificates via an FTP server, establishing a centralized repository for quick team access.','Successfully established a second lab resource, UL, for HP\'s CE RED Cybersecurity certification. This effectively reduced reliance on the single vendor, SUD, and enhanced lab resilience as well as flexibility in case allocation.','Acted as a strategic partner to clients by initiating proactive outreach 3-4 months in advance to notify them of upcoming certificate expirations, integrating End-of-Service date information. T