1,0,2025,'年底',''),(431,'11107012','加分工作項目','公共事務','同事請假時,幫忙協助處理工作事務.','參加定期周會,與同事分享討論project 上遇到問題及解決的方法.','與同事一同打掃,維護實驗室整潔.',3,'1','0','0',1,0,2025,'年底',''),(432,'10811055','日常工作項目','DM FY25 Series NPI Design & Debug','Led the RF NPI implementation for MegamindPG Intel platforms, covering noise debug, SVTP reports, and HP audits, ensuring design readiness and compliance.','Identified and delivered RF cost-saving opportunities for FY25 (L1/L2), and aligned RF solutions with HP customer to study cost-saving.','Ensured RAM/SSD OOC validation and HP SVTP compliance for HP rules, preventing schedule slips and quality issues, ensuring readiness for mass production without quality deviation.',3,'1','1','1',3,0,2025,'年底',''),(433,'10811055','日常工作項目','DM FY26 Series NPI Design & Debug','Executed multi-platform RF NPI implementation (Moomin/MoominPG/MoominPS/Moana) including noise debugging and HP auditing, enhancing overall NPI stability.','Conducted and proposed cost-saving RF solutions for SSD slot designs, supporting BU cost-saving planning.','Validated RF performance for QuiQon accessories (Studio V72/E70 with TC10), ensuring full compliance with HP RF standards.',3,'1','1','1',3,0,2025,'年底',''),(434,'10811055','日常工作項目','DM FY27 RFQ Study Support (Intel/AMD)','Delivered complete FY27 RFQ RF solution assessments with HP through feasibility analysis and simulation, enhancing competitiveness for upcoming RFQ bidding.','Recommended PFAS-FREE antenna materials that meet HP regulatory requirements, mitigating supplier compliance risk.','Assessed and optimized AMD RFIM strategies for different RF levels, resulting in improved RF performance readiness for RFQ goal.',3,'1','1','1',3,0,2025,'年底',''),(435,'10811055','AI的工作項目','AI Application Study','Research and demonstrate AI-based motion detection and simulation concepts, showing how sports applications reduce the need for physical labor and enhance exercise autonomy.\r(AI Fitness Personal Trainer)','AI and Python are being used